data.oai_dc:dc: File is structured so that there is one individual per line. Variable "chick.age" represents the age of the chick host used in weeks. "Response" is a binomial variable, where 1 = landing on the host, and 0 = no response. "time" represents time to landing in seconds. "landing.site" is a multinomial response, where h = head, b = breast, l = legs, w = wings, and t = tail feathers and rump. Landing site was only measure in no-choice tests where the chick was used.
